snippet.title: Elette Fragments Trailer 2020
snippet.description:
Steam Link: https://theindieaccord.com/games/elettefragments/
Discord: https://discord.gg/VjdZU4r
Twitter: https://twitter.com/TheIndieAccord

Join Benviolo, the axe wielding star of the play, and his comrades Mathias Jr and Juliet in this unique beat em up style game. Solve the mystery surrounding the island nation of Lotte in the years that follow the zombie invasion and the return of Queen Hermielle!

Music by: DARK FANTASY STUDIO and Nicolas Jeudy 

https://theindieaccord.com/games/elettefragments/

#theindieaccord
